---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Psychiatry — Program Requirements" description="RANZCP psychiatry training program, assessments, and examinations.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Program Requirements</h1>
    <p>Psychiatry — RANZCP</p>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Training Structure</h2>
    <p>Training occurs as a registrar under supervision of experienced psychiatrists in hospital and clinical settings across 3 stages over a minimum of 5 years.</p>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Rotations in hospitals and clinics</li>
      <li>Formal education course (mandatory)</li>
      <li>Workplace-based assessments throughout</li>
      <li>Clinical and written examinations</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Assessments</h2>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>Rotation assessments — completed at end of each rotation</li>
      <li>Entrustable Professional Activities (EPAs)</li>
      <li>Psychotherapy Written Case — in-depth case write-up</li>
      <li>Scholarly Project — research or quality improvement project</li>
      <li>Written examinations</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Fellowship Competencies</h2>
    <p>Training is guided by the RANZCP Fellowship Competencies framework, which outlines the knowledge, skills, and attributes required to practise as a consultant psychiatrist in Australia or Aotearoa New Zealand.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
